formula, because the mass is

00:41:56.140 --> 00:41:58.800
in the downstairs.

00:41:58.800 --> 00:42:02.240
Say, if you increase the mass,
then the temperature actually

00:42:02.240 --> 00:42:03.730
decrease.

00:42:03.730 --> 00:42:07.670
This is actually opposite
to your everyday experience.

00:42:07.670 --> 00:42:08.700
OK?

00:42:08.700 --> 00:42:10.880
Because when we
increase the mass,

00:42:10.880 --> 00:42:14.410
the black hole
temperature decreases.

00:42:14.410 --> 00:42:14.910
OK?

00:42:19.680 --> 00:42:26.030
If you calculate the,
