00:42:26.030 --> 00:42:29.950
the specific heat is
smaller than zero.

00:42:29.950 --> 00:42:31.240
OK.

00:42:31.240 --> 00:42:34.845
So we will later
see this is actually

00:42:34.845 --> 00:42:39.820
an artifact of a black hole in
asymptotically flat spacetime.

00:42:39.820 --> 00:42:42.660
So here, we're considering black
holes in asymptotically flat

00:42:42.660 --> 00:42:44.230
spacetime.

00:42:44.230 --> 00:42:46.590
If you think about black
