00:42:54.400 --> 00:42:55.710
As in the ordinary story.

00:42:55.710 --> 00:42:56.300
OK?

00:42:56.300 --> 00:42:59.810
So this is just
the third remark.

00:42:59.810 --> 00:43:05.460
So another third remark is that
