00:43:13.650 --> 00:43:18.360
but actually, those relations
apply to all black holes

00:43:18.360 --> 00:43:20.180
have been discovered.

00:43:20.180 --> 00:43:22.290
Just apply to every black hole.

00:43:22.290 --> 00:43:24.040
OK?

00:43:24.040 --> 00:43:27.130
So now let me talk about
