00:45:40.546 --> 00:45:41.920
for example, the
electric charge.

00:45:49.200 --> 00:45:50.977
For example, electric charge.

00:45:50.977 --> 00:45:52.470
OK?

00:45:52.470 --> 00:45:55.500
And so-- yeah, so
